title: Marvel Zombies Complete as of March 2009
description:
Every Marvel Zombies appearance I've come across.

I've tried to number the comics in order, there may be a few mistakes since the series jumps between dimensions.

Includes:

Army of Darkness #13
Marvel Zombies vs. Army of Darkness #1-5
Marvel Zombies, Dead Days
Ultimate Fantastic Four #21-23
Marvel Zombies #1-5
Ultimate Fantastic Four #30-32
Black Panther #27-30
Marvel Zombies 2 #1-5
Marvel Zombies 3 #1-4

Use CDisplay or Comical to read the files (.cbr) and enjoy!
